description:
Kate and Doree talk about how to politely say no to Multi-Level Marketing (MLMs) products and recommend natural deodorants that really work. They also respond to an email from a listener in her 30s who feels isolated in singlehood.

For more info, visit forever35podcast.com. To leave a voicemail, call 781-591-0390. You can also email the podcast at forever35podcast@gmail.com.

Theme music by Riot.
